"title": "5415: money, uses of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5415: money, uses of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Monetary transactions have taken place from the earliest biblical times. Originally precious metals were weighed out; coins were introduced later.</p>\n<h2>The first mention of money</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:12\">GEN 17:12</a></strong></p>\n<h2>The use of money</h2>\n<h3>For the purchase and sale of land</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen23:14-Gen23:15\">GEN 23:14–23:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:9-Jer32:10\">JER 32:9–32:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:7\">MAT 27:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:34\">ACT 4:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:1-Acts5:2\">ACT 5:1–5:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:16\">ACT 7:16</a></p>\n<h3>For the purchase and sale of food</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:57\">GEN 41:57</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen42:5\">GEN 42:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen42:35\">GEN 42:35</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs7:16\">2KI 7:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:5\">JHN 6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:7\">JHN 6:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:6\">REV 6:6</a></p>\n<h3>For other merchandise</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:11-Rev18:13\">REV 18:11–18:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:25\">GEN 37:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:13\">JAS 4:13</a></p>\n<h3>For religious offerings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod30:11-Exod30:16\">EXO 30:11–30:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num3:44-Num3:48\">NUM 3:44–3:48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:4-Deut12:6\">DEU 12:4–12:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs22:4-2Kgs22:6\">2KI 22:4–22:6</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr34:9-2Chr34:11\">2CH 34:9–34:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra7:15-Ezra7:17\">EZR 7:15–7:17</a></p>\n<h3>For gifts to the poor</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:9\">MAT 26:9</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:5\">MRK 14:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:5\">JHN 12:5</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:3\">ACT 3:3</a></p>\n<h3>For wages</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:2\">MAT 20:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:4\">JAS 5:4</a></p>\n<h3>For investment and moneylending</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:27\">MAT 25:27</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:23\">LUK 19:23</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:25\">EXO 22:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh5:10-Neh5:11\">NEH 5:10–5:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:34-Luke6:35\">LUK 6:34–6:35</a></p>\n<h3>For provision for the future</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl7:12\">ECC 7:12</a></p>\n<h3>For the settlement of disputes</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod21:8-Exod21:11\">EXO 21:8–21:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod21:35\">EXO 21:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:15\">EXO 22:15</a></p>\n<h3>For taxes</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:24\">MAT 17:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:15\">1KI 10:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh5:4\">NEH 5:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:17-Matt22:19\">MAT 22:17–22:19</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:15\">MRK 12:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:22-Luke20:24\">LUK 20:22–20:24</a></p>\n<h3>For tribute money</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs15:19-2Kgs15:20\">2KI 15:19–15:20</a></p>\n<h3>For the purchase of slaves</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev22:11\">LEV 22:11</a></p>\n<h3>For bribery</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth3:9\">EST 3:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:12-Matt28:13\">MAT 28:12–28:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts24:26\">ACT 24:26</a></p>\n<h3>Fortune-telling for money</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic3:11\">MIC 3:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:16\">ACT 16:16</a></p>\n<h3>Blood money</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:6\">MAT 27:6</a></p>\n<h2>Money changers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:12\">MAT 21:12</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:15\">MRK 11:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:14\">JHN 2:14</a></p>",
